      "content": "but what if i don't want to break the cycle? what if i just want the cycle to stop? i'm so tired of being told to \"live for myself\" when there's nothing left of me to live for. it feels like i'm just waiting for the clock to run out anyway. it would be so much easier to just let go and stop fighting the emptiness. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just... not be here anymore?",
